            <div class="terms-content">
                <h1>Affiliate Terms and Conditions</h1>
                <p class="lead">Last updated: July 4, 2025</p>

                <h2>Affiliate Program Overview</h2>
                <p>
                    Make Sure It Happens Inc ("MSIH") offers an affiliate program where qualified individuals can earn affiliate fees by promoting msih.org through their social networks using assigned referral codes. By participating in this program, you agree to these specific terms in addition to our general Terms of Service.
                </p>

