                <p>
                    For questions about the affiliate program, payment issues, or these terms, contact us at:
                    <br>
                    Email: affiliate@msih.org
                    <br>
                    Subject: Affiliate Program Inquiry
                </p>

                <div class="acceptance-notice mt-4 p-3 bg-light border-start border-primary border-4">
                    <p class="mb-0">
                        <strong>By participating in the MSIH affiliate program, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agree to be bound by these Affiliate Terms and Conditions.</strong>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
